    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray (or two!)<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>with non-stick baking paper</p><p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of<strong> flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a rolling pin and cut into 1 piece per person</p><p>Add the<strong> pastry </strong>to the tray[s] and score a 1cm border around the edge with the tip of a sharp knife</p><p>Tip: The pastry border will puff up to give you a nice crust!</p>",
