    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread the <strong>creamy leeks </strong>over the pastry (keep it within the borders!) then layer the<strong> cooked mushrooms </strong>over the top</p><p>Add the <strong>onion wedges </strong>to the tray[s] around the pastry</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the top part of the oven and cook for 15-18 min or until the pastry is cooked through, puffed up and golden – these are your<strong> leek & mushroom tarts</strong></p>",
