    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the<strong> </strong>tarts are cooking, slice your<strong> apple[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>into matchsticks (skin on)</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>apple matchsticks</strong>,<strong> walnuts</strong>,<strong> </strong>the <strong>remaining cider vinegar</strong>,<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>apple & walnut salad</strong></p>",
