    {
      "instruction": "<p>Carefully separate the<strong> roasted onion wedges</strong> into petals and add them to the apple & walnut salad</p><p>Serve the <strong>leek & mushroom tart </strong>with the<strong> apple & walnut salad </strong>and the <strong>roasted potatoes </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
